OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777385514
OL,3,CMedics called to Adam Johnson's fatal
OL,4,Cinjury found 'chaotic scene', hearing
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FParamedics who responded to the fatal
OL,8,Fneck injury suffered by a Nottingham
OL,9,FPanthers player said they found a
OL,10,F"chaotic scene", a coroner has said.
OL,12,FAdam Johnson, who was 29, was playing
OL,13,Ffor the Panthers against Sheffield
OL,14,FSteelers in an Elite League fixture,
OL,15,Fwhen he was hit in the neck by
OL,16,FSteelers player Matthew Petgrave's
OL,17,Fskate.
OL,19,FMr Johnson died in hospital following
OL,20,Fthe incident at Sheffield Arena in
OL,21,FOctober 2023.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@OO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
