OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777385514
OL,3,CMedics called to Adam Johnson's fatal
OL,4,Cinjury found 'chaotic scene', hearing
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FAt a pre-inquest review in Sheffield
OL,8,Ftoday (27 April), senior coroner
OL,9,FTanyka Rawden, told the hearing she
OL,10,Fhad seen statements from Yorkshire
OL,11,FAmbulance Service paramedics and said:
OL,13,F"Their evidence suggests they came
OL,14,Facross quite a chaotic scene."
OL,16,FShe also had "a lot of questions about
OL,17,Fhow Yorkshire Ambulance Service (YAS)
OL,18,Faccessed the ice".
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@^O]xD@NOUzD@QO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777385514
OL,3,CMedics called to Adam Johnson's fatal
OL,4,Cinjury found 'chaotic scene', hearing
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FShe said there is evidence from one
OL,8,Fparamedic who had to climb over the
OL,9,Fbarriers "because nobody could show
OL,10,Fthem onto the ice", and concerns over
OL,11,Fthe availability of blood to
OL,12,Fparamedics attending the incident.
OL,14,F"I cannot imagine what life has been
OL,15,Flike for all of you since Adam died"
OL,17,FMr Johnson's mother Sue and his
OL,18,Ffiancee Ryan Wolfe, were among family
OL,19,Fmembers who joined the hearing on a
OL,20,Fvideo link from the United States.
OL,26,@qD@JOUrD@RO]vD@AOUwD@dO]zD@Frr
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777385514
OL,3,CMedics called to Adam Johnson's fatal
OL,4,Cinjury found 'chaotic scene', hearing
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe coroner told them: "I'm sorry that
OL,8,Fwe are meeting in these circumstances."
OL,10,FShe said: "I cannot imagine what life
OL,11,Fhas been like for all of you since
OL,12,FAdam died."
OL,14,FShe further added: "It must have been
OL,15,Fhorrific for all of you."
OL,17,FLast year, the Crown Prosecution
OL,18,FService (CPS) decided it would not
OL,19,Fbring criminal charges against Matthew
OL,20,FPetgrave, who is Canadian.
OL,26,@oD@XOUpD@gO]rD@KOUtD@KO]vD@TOUwD@YO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777385514
OL,3,CMedics called to Adam Johnson's fatal
OL,4,Cinjury found 'chaotic scene', hearing
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FPetgrave's barrister, Michael Hayton
OL,8,FKC, told the hearing his client is
OL,9,Fcurrently in Canada.
OL,11,FThe coroner said she is planning to
OL,12,Fcall Mr Petgrave and nine other
OL,13,Fplayers from the match to give
OL,14,Fevidence, but this is under review, as
OL,15,Fnone of these players are currently in
OL,16,Fthe UK.
OL,18,F"I'm not going to rush this"
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777385514
OL,3,CMedics called to Adam Johnson's fatal
OL,4,Cinjury found 'chaotic scene', hearing
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FSenior coroner Tanyka Rawden said the
OL,8,Finquest will be heard in front of a
OL,9,Fjury and said "there is a lot CCTV" in
OL,10,Fthis case.
OL,12,FShe said: "Unfortunately ` and I say
OL,13,Fthat because it will be distressing
OL,14,Ffor them ` I think the jury is going
OL,15,Fto have to see some of the CCTV."
OL,17,FIt is unlikely that the inquest into
OL,18,FMr Johnson's death will take place
OL,19,Fthis year.
OL,26,@qD@OOUqD@cO]tD@KOUwD@aO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777385514
OL,3,CMedics called to Adam Johnson's fatal
OL,4,Cinjury found 'chaotic scene', hearing
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe coroner said she is aware there is
OL,8,Fpressure to hold it earlier but she
OL,9,Fpointed out that her investigation had
OL,10,Fto be paused until the police inquiry
OL,11,Fwas concluded last year.
OL,13,FShe said: "I'm not going to rush this.
OL,14,FI have to conduct a fair and fearless
OL,15,Finvestigation even if it takes time.
OL,17,F"I understand how difficult this is
OL,18,Ffor Adam's family. He died in October
OL,19,F2023 and we are now in April 2026.
OL,26,@uD@KOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/8
