OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1777385514
OL,3,CMedics called to Adam Johnson's fatal
OL,4,Cinjury found 'chaotic scene', hearing
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"I cannot imagine what it's been like
OL,8,Ffor them between these two dates."
OL,10,FA provisional date for another pre-
OL,11,Finquest review was set for 29 October.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
